lead_paragraph: Australian Olympic team members were forced to evacuate their lodgings on Friday at the Rio de Janeiro Olympics after a small fire in a basement parking area caused smoke to fill the stairwells.

headline.print_headline: Australia Evacuates Rio Olympic Lodging After Small Fire
